  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.11">
<l>ētta vēḻula kuṅkoṇṭa kōlak</l>
<l>kūtta ṉaikkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>vāynta vāyirat tuḷḷivai pattuṭa</l>
<l>ṉētta vallārk killaiyō rūṉamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those able to praise</l>
<l>with these ten among the excellent thousand</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr on the beautiful</l>
<l>dancer who took the seven worlds while they were praising</l>
	<l>the will be no deficiency.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
